            "question_1": "Description",
            "answer_1": "<p><strong>Advanced Recovery Complex </strong>is a thoughtfully formulated supplement designed to support your body's natural <br/>wellness processes, joint health, and gut integrity.<br/><br/>Each capsule delivers a premium amino acid complex in  bioavailable form — designed to support your body's natural processes and daily comfort.<br/><br/>Third-party tested. Easy daily capsules. Designed to support your body's natural processes. These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.</p>",
            "question_2": "Why You Need KineThera(C) Advanced Recovery Complex?",
            "answer_2": "<p>If you're tired of daily wellness support that complements your active lifestyle-Advanced Recovery Complex was designed for you.</p><p>This daily formula is designed to support your body's natural processes, promote resilience, and help you feel your best-backed by a commitment to quality and your satisfaction.</p>",
            "question_3": "Benefits",
            "answer_3": "<p> Supports daily comfort and joint flexibility</p><p> Promotes overall daily wellness</p><p> Supports gut health and digestive comfort</p><p> Designed to support your body's natural processes</p><p> Easy-to-swallow capsules (no injections required)</p><p> Third-party tested, free from fillers & artificial additives</p>",
            "question_4": "Recommended Use",
            "answer_4": "<p>Take 1 capsule twice daily with food<br/>(morning and evening work best).</p><p><br/><strong>Consistency matters more than timing</strong>-<br/>regular daily use supports your wellness<br/>routine. Compatible with your existing supplement routine.</p>",
            "question_5": "Do You Offer A Guarantee?",
            "answer_5": "<p>Yes! All our products are backed by our full 60-day money-back guarantee.<br/><br/>If you aren't completely satisfied, simply contact us — we'll make it right, no questions asked.</p>",
