          "settings": {
            "show_stars": true,
            "title": "Finally something that actually works for my routine.",
            "content": "<p>I've tried a lot of supplements over the years and most just sat on my shelf. Been taking this every morning with breakfast for about 3 weeks now. I actually look forward to it. Energy feels more consistent throughout the day and my digestion has been noticeably better. Will definitely be reordering.</p>",
